      "text": "investigating the action of drugs:"
    },
    {
      "line": 20,
      "text": "how they are discovered, what"
    },
    {
      "line": 21,
      "text": "they are, what they do, how they"
    },
    {
      "line": 22,
      "text": "can be helpful - or harmful. But"
    },
    {
      "line": 23,
      "text": "my interests lie somewhat out-"
    },
    {
      "line": 24,
      "text": "side the mainstream of pharma-"
    },
    {
      "line": 25,
      "text": "cology. The area | have found"
