      "text": "psychedelic drugs (compounds"
    },
    {
      "line": 28,
      "text": "which temporarily alter the"
    },
    {
      "line": 31,
      "text": "state of one’s consciousness)."
    },
    {
      "line": 34,
      "text": "The prevailing opinion in this"
    },
    {
