      "text": "either relatively safe or at least"
    },
    {
      "line": 40,
      "text": "have acceptable risks, and there"
    },
    {
      "line": 41,
      "text": "are other drugs that are illegal"
    },
    {
      "line": 42,
      "text": "and have no legitimate place in"
    },
    {
      "line": 43,
      "text": "our society. Although this opinion"
    },
